data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Summer Lake Subdivision on a full finished basement! Nestled at 2068 Reserve Parkway, this beautiful residence boasts 4 beds, 3.5 baths, and a 2-car garage. Step inside to find an inviting atmosphere with a formal dining room, open kitchen with a kitchenette, and a family den area. The deck overlooks a large backyard, perfect for relaxing and entertaining while listening to the nearby lake's ducks. The master suite features a separate shower and Jacuzzi tub. Enjoy HOA amenities including 2 pools, a tennis court, and a playground. Call for more info!
